    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individue Trinitatis, anno domini nostri Iesu Christi
                        millesimo centesimo septuagesimo sexto, regnante
                            Frederico dei gratia Romanorum <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperatore</rs> et semper
                        augusto, quarto ydus martii, indictione VIIII, <rs key="#Copyist"
                            >exemplar</rs> antiqui instrumenti factum. In nomine sancte et individue
                        Trinitatis. Anno ab incarnatione eiusdem domini nostri Iesu Christi
                        millesimo centesimo octavo, sextodecimo kalendarum octubris, indictione
                        prima, et ideo in dei nomine ego quidem domina <persName key="#Countess" ref="#people/125"
                            >Matilda</persName>, inclita <rs key="#Countess">comitissa</rs>, filia donni <persName key="#Marquis/duke"
                            ref="#people/1">Bonifatii</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchionis</rs>, per cartulam precariam atque emphyteotecariam iuris
                        nomine concedo vobis <persName><name>Yldebrando</name></persName> iugera
                        duo; et <persName><name ref="Wido">Guido</name></persName> germani iugera
                        duo; <persName><name>Ogizone</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Yldebrando</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Wido">Guido</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name ref="Sichinzo">Sigezo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Umbertus">Uberto</name></persName> germani
                        iugera duo; <persName><name>Aczo</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Sichinzo">Sigezo</name></persName> germani,
                                <persName><name ref="Alfredus">Alfredum</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Albertus">Albertus</name></persName> germani, <persName><name
                                ref="Martinus">Martinus</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name ref="Gregorius">Gregorio</name></persName> iugero duo;
                                <persName><name ref="Lambertus">Lanbertus</name></persName> de
                        <persName><name ref="Bonaldus">Bonardo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Albertus">Alberto</name></persName> de <rs key="#Priest">presbitero</rs>
                        <persName><name ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> de
                        <persName><name ref="Severus">Severo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName> germani et
                        <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Albareto</placeName> de
                            <persName><name>Roczo</name></persName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Restano</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name ref="Dominicus">Dominico</name></persName> et
                        <persName><name ref="Dominicus">Dominico</name></persName> de
                        <persName><name ref="Maginardus">Maginardo</name></persName>,
                        <persName><name ref="Albertus">Alberto</name></persName> de <placeName>Sancto
                            Iohanne</placeName> iugera duo;
                        <persName><name ref="Martinus">Martinus</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Aczo</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Omizo</name></persName> iugerum unum;
                        <persName><name ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Raginbaldo</name></persName> et
                        <persName><name ref="Lambertus">Lamberto</name></persName> iugerum unum;
                        <persName><name ref="Albertus/Candidus">Alberto Candido</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petro</name></persName> germani et
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus de Gaiolo">Petro</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Gaiule</placeName>, <persName><name ref="Albertus">Alberto</name></persName>
                        et <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohanne</name></persName> et
                        <persName><name ref="Albertus">Albertus</name></persName>
                        nepos eorum iugera duo; <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>
                        filius <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName> faber et
                                <persName><name ref="Andreas/Stanperto">Andrea Stanperto</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Dominicus">Dominico</name></persName> germani,
                        <persName><name ref="Dominicus">Dominico</name></persName> de presbitero
                        <persName><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName> iugera duo;
                        <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName> faber et
                        <persName><name ref="Martinus">Martino</name></persName> et
                        <persName><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName> et
                        <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName> nepos eorum iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Bonando</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Steuuzo</name></persName>,
                        <persName><name ref="Albertus">Alberto</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Beneventano</name></persName>,
                        <persName><name ref="Andreas">Andrea</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Pregite</name></persName> iugera duo;
                        <persName><name ref="Gherardus">Girardo</name></persName> de
                        <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petro</name></persName> de
                        <persName><name ref="Vitale">Vitale</name></persName> et
                        <persName><name ref="Albertus">Alberto</name></persName> de
                        <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohanne</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Gotolo</name></persName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Savorecto</name></persName> et
                        <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Pregite</name></persName> iugera duo;
                        <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Bononio</name></persName> et
                        <persName><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName> de
                        <persName><name ref="Sicardus">Sicardo</name></persName> iugera duo;
                        <persName><name ref="Marco">Marco</name></persName> de
                        <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohanne</name></persName> de
                        <persName><name ref="Ragibertushannes">Ragiberto</name></persName>,
                        <persName><name ref="Albertus">Alberto</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Formigine</placeName> iugera duo;
                        <persName><name ref="Albertus">Alberto</name></persName> de
                        <persName><name ref="Ermengarda">Ermengarda</name></persName> et
                        <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName> germani,
                        <persName><name ref="Petrus/Suxinaro">Petrus Suxinaro</name></persName> iugera duo;
                        <persName><name ref="Gherardus">Girardo</name></persName> canauaro iugerum unum;
                                <persName><name>Bonellus</name></persName> bovulcus iurerum unum;
                                <persName><name>Rodulfus</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Engelbertus</name></persName> unum,
                        <persName><name ref="Dominicus">Dominico</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Fontana</placeName> et
                        <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Albertus/Prilingarde">Alberto
                                Prilingarde</name></persName> II,
                            <persName><name>Stefanus</name></persName>
                        <rs>diaconus</rs> et <persName><name ref="Albertus">Alberto</name></persName> germani,
                                <persName><name>Everardo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Bonvisino</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Iohannes</name></persName> iugera duo,
                                <persName><name>Arduino</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Ugo</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Teuzo</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name>Lanfranco</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Petro</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Carbone</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Rodaldo</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name>Alberto</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Petro</name></persName> germani de
                            <placeName>Nugareto</placeName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Ragimundo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Guido</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Alberto</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Petro</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Leo</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name>Giberto</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Carbone</name></persName> germani,
                                <persName><name>Lamberto</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Bernardo</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Carbone</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Gontardo</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Girardo</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Carbone</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Guarino</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Petro</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Gandulfo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Girardo</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Alberto</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Guido</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Iohannes</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Ioannino</name></persName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Guido</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Petro</name></persName> germani et
                                <persName><name>Dagiberto</name></persName> iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Petrus Longobardus</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Iohannes</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Guido</name></persName> montario et
                                <persName><name>Girardo Pavanese</name></persName> iugera duo,
                                <persName><name>Goctefredo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Amacza</name></persName> villano iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Dominico</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Blanco</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Azo</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Carbone</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name>Petro</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Alberto</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                                <persName><name>Girardus</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Stefanus</name></persName> germani iugera duo;
                        namque <persName><name>Rollando</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Aco</name></persName> in tertiam portionem de duo
                        iugera, <persName><name>Ingezoni</name></persName> aliam tertiam, sitque
                                <persName><name>Girardo</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Teuzoni</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Stefano</name></persName> in tertiam;
                                <persName><name>Iohannes Favaro</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Andrea</name></persName> in tertiam partem de duobus
                        iugera et <persName><name>Gregorius</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Ildebrando</name></persName> in duabus partibus;
                        scilicet in vos et in vestris heredibus usque in perpetuum. Que autem iam
                        dicta iugera sunt in <rs>curte</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/1566"><geogName ref="#estates/1126"
                                >Celula</geogName></placeName>, quorum vocabula sunt curte de
                            <geogName ref="#estates/1131"><placeName ref="#places/1577"
                                >Paulecla</placeName></geogName> et curte de <placeName
                            ref="#places/2480"><geogName ref="#estates/1127"
                            >Radigosa</geogName></placeName>, et in curte <geogName
                            ref="#estates/1130"><placeName ref="#places/1575"
                            >Gisso</placeName></geogName> et in aliis locis, ubicumque nunc date
                        sunt vel inantea date erunt tantummodo ad habendum, tenendum, fruendum,
                        fatiendum, quicquid vobis utile erit, eo videlicet modo, ut <rs>roccam</rs>
                        de <placeName ref="#places/1576"><geogName ref="#estates/1132"
                                >Gissadello</geogName></placeName>, pro qua hec omnia do vobis, ab
                        hac ora inantea incastellare, guitare et laborare et claudere debetis, sicut
                        decet et conveniens erit, ita ut omni anno de mense martio denariorum
                        Veneticorum persolvere debeatis per unumquemque iugerum ad <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/47"><placeName ref="#places/15">ecclesiam sancti
                                Silvestri</placeName></orgName> usque in perpetuum. Si vero predicta
                        rocca permanserit et si domina Matilda in aliquo modo eam reliquerit vel
                        vastaverit sine ulla occasione, que fieri potest, predictam cartulam
                        deinceps permaneat usque in perpetuum. Et promitto ego domina predicta
                        Matilda tam pro me quam pro meos successores vobis supradictis petitoris vel
                        vestris heredibus usque in perpetuo defensare auctorizare. Si qua vero pars,
                        qui contra hanc paginam emphyteotecaria ire temptaverint et non
                        observaverint omnia, quod superius legitur, tunc componat illa pars, qui hoc
                        non observaverint, ad partem fidem servantem pene nomine solidi centum
                        denariorum Lucensium, et post penam solutam cartulam precariam maneat in sua
                        firmitate. Actum in loco <placeName ref="#places/269">sancti
                            Cesarii</placeName>. Supra legitur: Matilda dei gratia, si quid est,
                        subscripsi. Ego <persName><name>Daniel</name></persName>
                        <placeName ref="#places/446">Montebelliensis</placeName>
                        <rs>archipresbiter</rs>
                        <rs key="#Witness">interfui</rs>. <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name>Ubaldo</name></persName> de <placeName>Scoveto</placeName> et
                        + <persName key="#Witness"><name>Ugizone</name></persName> filius
                                <persName><name>Ragineri</name></persName>. <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name>Gandulfo</name></persName> da <placeName>Broilo</placeName>
                        namque + <persName key="#Witness"><name>Rodulfo</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Monte Claro</placeName> rogati sunt. Ego <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name>Conon</name></persName> subscripsi et fieri rogavi.
                        Ego <persName key="#Witness" ref="#people/3502">Iohannes</persName> dictus
                            <rs>prior</rs> vidi et scripsi. In dei nomine, ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Tabellio"><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellio</rs> hanc cartulam precariam, sicut superius
                        legitur, <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs> et complevi. Dominus <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name>Nicholaus</name></persName> et dominus <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name>Zaccarus</name></persName>
                        <rs>iudices</rs> de <rs>comuni</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/7"><orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1119"
                                >Bononie</orgName></placeName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name>Pegoloctus</name></persName>
                        <rs>causidicus</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"
                            ><name>Ardicono</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name>Rainerius</name></persName> de
                            <persName><name>Petro</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name>Aldizone</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name>Zuccherus</name></persName> ad hanc cartam antiquam et novam
                        audiendam interfuere et huius rei causa testes vocati sunt. Ego <persName
                            key="#Copyist #Notary"><name>Ugo</name></persName> dei gratia comunis
                        Bononie <rs>notarius</rs> hoc presens instrumentum, ut vidi in antiquo,
                        subscripsi et firmavi.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
